据人民日报消息，世界卫生组织10日公布最新数据显示，截至欧洲中部时间10日10时（北京时间10日17时），中国以外新冠肺炎确诊病例较前一日增加4105例，达到32778例；中国以外死亡病例较前一日增加186例，达到872例。
According to the People's Daily, the World Health Organization (WHO) reported on Thursday that the number of confirmed cases of pneumonia in non-Chinese territory had increased by 4,105 cases to 32,778 as compared with the previous day, and the number of deaths outside China had increased by 186 cases to 872, the daily said.
另据世界教科文组织消息，新冠肺炎疫情的蔓延已致多国实施停课措施，全球从学前教育到高等教育阶段近3.63亿学生受到影响。
According to UNESCO, the spread of the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic has led to the suspension of classes in many countries, affecting nearly 363 million students worldwide, from pre-primary to higher education.
意大利累计确诊超万例 死亡631例根据当地时间3月10日18时意大利卫生部公布的最近数据，意大利现有新冠病毒患者8514例，死亡631例，治愈1004例，累计确诊感染新冠病毒总人数为10149例，较3月9日18时新增977例，新增168例死亡病例。
Italy has 8,514 new cases of Crested Virus, 631 deaths and 1,004 cures, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 10,149, an increase of 977 from 18.00 on March 9 and 168 new deaths, according to the latest figures released by the Italian Ministry of Health on March 10, 2006.
意大利总理孔特9日晚发表电视讲话表示，为避免新冠肺炎疫情进一步扩散，自10日起在全国范围内实施封城。
Italy's Prime Minister Jose Antonio Conte said in a televised speech Tuesday night that a nationwide ban had been imposed since October 10 to prevent the outbreak from spreading further.
除可证明的工作、健康和紧急需求三种特殊原因，全国范围内的民众不得擅自离开所在地。
People throughout the country may not leave the territory without authorization for three special reasons: demonstrable work, health and emergency needs.
在加强防疫措施的同时，意大利也在积极寻找外援。
Italy is actively seeking foreign aid while intensifying its preventive measures.
据外交部网站10日晚消息，国务委员兼外长王毅应约同意大利外长迪马约通电话。
State Councilor and Foreign Minister Wang Yi spoke by telephone with Italian Foreign Minister Didier Di Majoor, the Foreign Ministry reported Tuesday night.
迪马约表示，当前意大利疫情形势十分严峻，意政府正密切关注和学习中方抗疫的成功经验，采取有力举措阻止疫情扩散。
"The current situation in Italy is very serious," he said. "The Italian government is closely monitoring and learning from China's successful experience in fighting the epidemic and taking vigorous measures to stop its spread.
意方面临医疗物资和设备短缺的困难，希中方帮助解决燃眉之急。
Italy faces a shortage of medical supplies and equipment difficulties, hope that China will help meet the immediate needs.
王毅表示，虽然目前中方自身对医疗物资还有较大需求，但我们将克服困难，向意方提供口罩等医疗物资援助，加大力度向意出口急需的物资和设备。
Wang said that although China still needs medical materials on its own, we will overcome difficulties, provide medical supplies such as masks to the Italian side and step up efforts to export urgently needed materials and equipment to Italy.
如意方需要，中方也愿意派出医疗小组赴意协助抗疫。
If desired, China is willing to send medical teams to assist in the fight against the epidemic.
英国卫生部长确诊新冠肺炎据人民日报消息，英国卫生部长纳丁·多里斯已确诊感染新冠肺炎。
British Health Minister Nadine Doris has been confirmed to be infected with pneumonia, the People's Daily reported.
据了解，她曾在过去的一周内在议会与上百人会面，并且与英国首相约翰逊在唐宁街10号一同参加了招待会。
She is understood to have met hundreds of people in parliament over the past week and attended a reception with British Prime Minister Johnson at 10 Downing Street.
报道指出，多里斯在上周五（6日）出现症状，并在当地时间10日晚确诊。
Reported that Doris appeared on Friday (6) symptoms, and local time on the night of the diagnosis.
希腊宣布关闭境内所有学校据中国日报报道，希腊总理米佐塔基斯当地时间3月10日下午宣布，政府听取有关专家建议，决定关闭境内所有学校和大学14天，以控制新冠病毒的传播。
Greece closes all schools in Greece Greek Prime Minister Mitsotakis announced on the afternoon of March 10 that the government had listened to expert advice and decided to close all schools and universities in Greece for 14 days to control the spread of the new cap virus, China Daily reported.
米佐塔基斯强调，希腊政府将利用这14天全力减缓新冠肺炎疫情的蔓延、增强希腊医护能力。
Mr Mitsotakis stressed that the Greek government would use the 14 days to try to slow the spread of pneumonia in Greece and strengthen its health-care capacity.
截至3月10日下午，希腊已确诊89例，无死亡病例。
As of the afternoon of 10 March, 89 cases had been confirmed in Greece, with no deaths.
西班牙新冠肺炎确诊病例增至1695例截至当地时间10日22时，西班牙新冠肺炎患者达到1695例，死亡35例。
The number of confirmed cases of pneumonia in Spain rose to 1,695. By 2200 local time, 1,695 cases and 35 deaths had been reported in Spain.
其中首都马德里最为严重，患者数量达782例。
Madrid is the capital, with 782 cases.
为了遏制迅速发展的疫情，西班牙政府10日宣布多项举措，包括3月11日至3月25日间，暂停所有西班牙和意大利间的直航航班，西体育赛事均改为闭门举行等。
The Spanish government announced a number of measures to curb the rapid development of the epidemic, including the suspension of all direct flights between Spain and Italy between March 11 and March 25, and the transformation of Spanish sports events into closed doors.
此外，西众议院一名议员10日也确认感染新冠病毒，众议院宣布将在未来一周内休会。
In addition, a member of the Western House of Representatives confirmed the infection on the 10th, the House of Representatives announced that the next week will recess.
来源：中国青年报综合人民日报（记者 韩硕）、央视新闻（记者 魏帆）、海外网、中国日报、外交部官网等。
Sources: China Youth Daily (reporter Han Asus), CCTV News (reporter Wei Fan), Overseas Web, China Daily, Foreign Ministry website, etc.
